    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382710/extras/43689ee4a54aaf56fbeeea2ba45b5d92.poster.avif?t=1753809188\" width=616 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382710/extras/43689ee4a54aaf56fbeeea2ba45b5d92.webm?t=1753809188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382710/extras/43689ee4a54aaf56fbeeea2ba45b5d92.mp4?t=1753809188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>No matter if rabbit or hare, it's always puzzling!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After enjoying a whole day playing outside, it's time to go home. And there's no time to waste, be clever and try to do it in the minimum number of moves!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hare 136 is a simple and relaxing but increasingly challenging sliding puzzle game where you find the best path to move rabbits across the board. You can choose between the two available game modes: <strong>&quot;Slider&quot;</strong> where you try to get one of the rabbits back into their den, and <strong>&quot;Sower&quot;</strong> where you try to get the rabbits go through every tile to seed the whole map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Two game modes</strong>: Choose between <strong>Slider</strong> and <strong>Sower</strong>, where you use the sliding mechanic to reach different goals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>136 unique levels for each mode</strong>: Those are 272 unique levels in total!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Daily puzzle mode</strong>: If 272 levels weren't enough, you can come back tomorrow to get a completely new random level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Cute hand-drawn artstyle</strong>: The rabbits are cute and fluffy, so are the puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>An amazing soundtrack</strong>: If you ever wondered how rabbits and puzzles sound, this is how.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Steam achievements</strong>: A digital trophy for all the puzzles you are able to solve.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Slide rabbits, Solve Puzzles!</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382710/extras/0b6f297a47a856d259c56a14c2157165.poster.avif?t=1753809188\" width=616 height=594 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382710/extras/0b6f297a47a856d259c56a14c2157165.webm?t=1753809188\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2382710/extras/0b6f297a47a856d259c56a14c2157165.mp4?t=1753809188\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
